<P>
Photo, Perfect harmony -- Sam's Rhythm holds off Sassy Slew (8) to win sixth 
race at Santa Anita Saturday, her fourth victory in seven career starts. It was 
second of four consecutive victories for jockey Chris McCarron. JAVIER MENDOZA 
/ Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
