<P>
LEGISLATION -- UNITED STATES; TELEPHONE NUMBERS; TELEPHONE CALLS; TELEPHONE 
EQUIPMENT; PRIVACY; TELEPHONE INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
