from midnight to 1, has been described as a "comedy hour of unpredictable 
events, supported by a family of regular comedy players and guest stars." Dees, 
who has been at KIIS since 1982, has had one of the top-rated morning shows for 
the past six years. He also hosts the syndicated "The Weekly Top 40," which 
airs on more than 300 radio stations. CLAUDIA PUIG 
