ROTHENBERG, DAVID; SURVEILLANCE; ASSAULTS -- ORANGE COUNTY; ELECTRONIC 
EQUIPMENT; FEAR; COMPLAINTS; OAKLAND (CA) -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS 
