<TEXT>
<P>
Two exhibits at the Laguna Art Museum have been extended. "The Spiritual 
Series: Dan Lutz and the American Scene" will continue at the museum's main 
site in Laguna Beach through Feb. 25, and "Paul Kos: BER LIN," at the museum's 
South Coast Plaza satellite site, will continue through April 29. 
